intersection to William Hilton Parkway/Hwy 278, turn

You will be driving along the coast line passing Fuengirola, El Faro, La Cala de Mijas, Riviera, Calahonda, Cabopino and Las Chapas. Once you pass Las Chapas area, the Resort exit is getting near. The Resort is located in the area called Elviria. After Repsol Gas Station on your left take Elviria exit and from the roundabout cross over the bridge towards sea side. At next roundabout continue straight forward. At next roundabout take third exit.
Continue straight until you see Don Carlos Hotel you see Don Carlos Hotel entrance in front. Follow the road leaving Don Carlos hotel on your left. When you reach the next roundabout, take 1st exit downhill towards the ocean following the sign to Marriott's Marbella Beach resort. The Resort entrance is on your right hand side approximately 100 meters down. Reminder: Do not leave personal belongings in your vehicle.

Hotel on left.

A-7 (Motorway) or continue towards Algeciras/Marbella AP-7 (Toll Road). In Marbella the two roads will re-connect and form the A-7 again. Take the exit Cancelada / Cambio de sentido, take the roundabout for ¾ and cross the bridge to the next roundabout direction Marbella/Malaga. Join the A-7 in the opposite direction and after 2 Km take the first exit after the Senator Banus Spa Hotel, El Presidente Km168. If you are using GPS you can enter these details in system to find Playa Andaluza better: N(+) 36.46501 W(-) 5.01755 Tom Tom : N3628.038' W501.080' NOTE: For your convenience we recommend to take the Toll Road (AP-7) as it will be faster.

drivingDirection: Upon exiting Myrtle Bch Int'l Airport, go to 17 Bypass. Turn right on 17 Bypass towards North Myrtle Bch. Stay on 17 Bypass, turn right on 82nd Ave North (Parkway). The hotel is the first driveway on the left.

After exiting the airport grounds continue until the traffic light and turn right. Follow the main road (route 30). On your way you will pass the Nisky Shopping Center on the right, next you will pass the Total Gas station on your left, following the Banco Popular on your left and the Texaco Gas station on your left. Cross over and continue straight ahead, Marriott's Frenchman's Cove will be +/- ½ mile on your right.

drivingDirection: Exit the Airport and make a right at the light. Continue on this road for several miles as you drive on the waterfront. You will pass a police station at a light on your left. At the next light, make a right. You will pass "Yacht Haven Grande" on your right. At the second light, continue straight into "Havensight." At the top of the hill make a left. Stay on this for several miles. You will pass "Iggies" on your right and then "Gas Works." When you come to a "T" at the "Bridge to Nowhere," make a right. Continue on this road as you pass "Food Center" on your left. About a quarter of a mile after the National Armory make a right up a small hill. If you pass the high school on your left you have gone too far. Continue straight on this road and pass The Ritz-Carlton<sup>®</sup> Hotel. The entrance to The Ritz-Carlton Club<sup>®</sup> will be shortly after. *Remember to stay on the left!

Take the Beachline Expressway/State Road 528 to exit 1 for International Drive. Turn left onto International Drive and continue to Westwood Boulevard. Turn right and follow the boulevard approximately two miles. Property is located on the left side of the road.

drivingDirection: From Denver International Airport: West on I-70, approximately 135 miles to Exit 173. Turn right and follow the traffic circle completely around. Go under the highway, follow the second traffic circle halfway. Turn right and proceed over the bridge (you should see the Marriott sign directly in front of you). Bear right up the driveway and follow the signs to the registration area in the clubhouse.
